        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for information on weeping trees; asks for a few weeping elm seeds.</p>
            <p>The double peach is in flower; the almond has not flowered; will beg a specimen of fruit later.</p>
            <p>Has been unwell.</p>
            <p>Tells of Hooker’s admiration for TR’s articles.</p>
        </abstract>
